OL,3,CAlleged school knife attacker aged 13
OL,4,Cto face Old Bailey trial
OL,6,FA 13-year-old boy who allegedly
OL,7,Fstabbed two boys in the neck and
OL,8,Fsquirted another with insect spray in
OL,9,Fa school attack faces an Old Bailey
OL,10,Ftrial in the autumn.
OL,12,FThe child, who cannot be identified
OL,13,Ffor legal reasons, bit his nails and
OL,14,Fspoke only to confirm his name during
OL,15,Fhis first Crown Court hearing on
OL,16,FFriday before Mrs Justice Cheema-Grubb.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/3
