CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772204160
OL,3,CAlleged school knife attacker aged 13
OL,4,Cto face Old Bailey trial
OL,6,FHe is accused of launching an attack
OL,7,Fin front of numerous children and a
OL,8,Fteacher at Kingsbury High School in
OL,9,FBrent, north-west London, on February
OL,10,F10.
OL,12,FHe was charged with two counts of
OL,13,Fattempted murder and unlawfully and
OL,14,Fmaliciously administering a noxious
OL,15,Fthing to a third child.
OL,17,FHe has also been charged with
OL,18,Fpossession of a knife on school
OL,19,Fpremises without good reason or lawful
OL,20,Fauthority.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/3
