PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772204160
OL,3,CAlleged school knife attacker aged 13
OL,4,Cto face Old Bailey trial
OL,6,FDuring the hearing Mrs Justice Cheema-
OL,7,FGrubb set a timetable for the case and
OL,8,Fconfirmed it would be heard by a High
OL,9,FCourt judge at the Old Bailey.
OL,11,FA plea hearing will take place on July
OL,12,F3 and a trial lasting up to three
OL,13,Fweeks will start on November 23.
OL,15,FThe defendant, whose father attended
OL,16,Fthe hearing, was remanded into custody.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/3
